CustomField.description: This field is used in reporting to allow the number of advice records to be counted. This is used in helping us identify which advice meetings to send for review by our compliance partner.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This field is used in reporting to allow the number of advice records to be counted. This is used in helping us identify which advice meetings to send for review by our compliance partner. The value is always 1.
CustomField.label: One
